root.title: 🐣🐣Flappy bird Multiplayeouton!
root.content: Finally!!! Flappy bird Multiplayer/Pvp version is online for you. Download and play with your friends now! New version features: ▶1, Invite your friend to play with you, in real-time map scene, you and your friends. ▶2, Play with other players, auto-matched by Game center. ▶3, Get coins and PvP points by defeating your match. ▶4, No crashes and lagging.
